{
  "stem": "22586.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That they're risking their own lives and their families' lives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in April--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "April 1945.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't stay very long then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't stay long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We stayed long enough until his wife came back and daughters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we met them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and they were equally nice, wonderful, wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "None at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but we left shortly after the liberation and went to-- my sister and I went to work for the UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the United Nations Relief [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Association, I suppose, or what?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't what the A stands for.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Essen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Essen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Essen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, we worked in their house-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my-- Agnes Konigsberg and I stayed together and work for the UNRRA, kept house for them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my sister Elizabeth and Rene stayed-- now, I don't remember what they did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember then what they did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we-- we separated because the Konigsberg girls didn't want to stay together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they preferred that Agnes stayed with me and-- and Rene stayed with my sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we did that for a short time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then my sister and I got a job working for the North German Coal Control.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were working as receptionists there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the two Konigsberg girls went to work at an officer's club in Mulheim, Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we stayed in--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were still in Essen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the North German Coal Control was located in [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kruppvilla. ?] This was a magnificent, magnificent building, gorgeous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was mainly a-- an English-- the Essen and-- and the Ruhr area of Germany was occupied by British.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the North German Coal Control was a British organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
